  "description": "Both voices on VA square with different pulse widths — Voice 1 at PW 0.28, Voice 2 at PW 0.72 (mirror positions). In LOVE at +0.55, the spectral blend of the two asymmetric square waves creates a pulse-width modulation effect without an LFO — the blend IS the modulation. Mod envelope slowly sweeps the algoParam of Voice 2, shifting its harmonic emphasis. The cephalofoil: two eyes seeing different things, merged into one perception.",
